I have been researching this shawl for a bit now but have only found alot of contrary missimformation. My guild does not hunt in SG so I have not been able to go scout there but I know that if I steer them to where it drops they would gladly help me.  <br>
Anyone here have one that is willing to share how it is acquired? I am specifically looking to find out what mob dropped it, how often, where in SG and what type of force you need to get there and take them down. Any advice is appreciated.<br>
